This paper is primarily focused on face detection, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also discusses the need for further research and improvement in this area, which suggests that it could also fall under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The dataset creation and analysis aspects of the paper could also potentially fall under the multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR) categories, respectively.
